{"tid":2339292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：今日是平安夜，相信大家都會留在家中安渡佳節","createTime":"2020-12-24T14:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T16:53:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":11,"dislike":336,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c0a0480d8269c302f8fb2e2ddf7ce0fc24f07a","tid":2339292,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:05:01.000Z","msg":"今日是平安夜，由於疫情嚴峻和嚴格遵守社交距離的需要，相信大家都會留在家中安渡佳節。我祝願全港巿民身體健康，香港早日走出「疫」境，經濟和社會活動可以逐步恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n過去一年多，香港經歷了種種挑戰，或許有人會對前景擔心。我今年的聖誕賀卡展示了香港的十大著名標記，它們見證了香港的成功蛻變，亦將帶領香港在金融、商業、創科、旅遊、文化等各方面的未來發展。<br />\n<br />\n請大家先考考自己的眼光，把十個標記找出來，再核對在另一張圖片的答案。<br />\n<br />\n各位在家迎接聖誕新年的同時，請為所有抗疫的醫護和前線人員點讚👍👍！<br />\n<br />\n#同心抗疫 #走出疫境 #林鄭月娥 #CarrieLam<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99fc40f82de878df0587eddf1aad064e347ad43","tid":2339292,"uid":288304,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"60f2e63a2b1cd863fd89910160549bf7d884c7e5","tid":2339292,"uid":93600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0648594d9833e90896c343900bb64005014e14ba","tid":2339292,"uid":21470,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:05:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"a56d10d5ea3e60a650396bb4e9551599be9e938f","tid":2339292,"uid":93600,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:05:58.000Z","msg":"係困在家中"},{"pid":"e993dfc8c013b9e795c3e21da7526df00d2f87e0","tid":2339292,"uid":58335,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:05:59.000Z","msg":"串鳩連登仔冇街去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de16b12f57aa3974d1a9bcab3aff69f966ef73c5","tid":2339292,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":43,"score":-39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Qq84ig.jpg\" data