26,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:05:01.000Z","msg":"今日是平安夜，由於疫情嚴峻和嚴格遵守社交距離的需要，相信大家都會留在家中安渡佳節。我祝願全港巿民身體健康，香港早日走出「疫」境，經濟和社會活動可以逐步恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n過去一年多，香港經歷了種種挑戰，或許有人會對前景擔心。我今年的聖誕賀卡展示了香港的十大著名標記，它們見證了香港的成功蛻變，亦將帶領香港在金融、商業、創科、旅遊、文化等各方面的未來發展。<br />\n<br />\n請大家先考考自己的眼光，把十個標記找出來，再核對在另一張圖片的答案。<br />\n<br />\n各位在家迎接聖誕新年的同時，請為所有抗疫的醫護和前線人員點讚👍👍！<br />\n<br />\n#同心抗疫 #走出疫境 #林鄭月娥 #CarrieLam<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:07:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭西"},{"pid":"bbf823aaaa8ebc0dd234f151484b2c05aeab3060","tid":2339292,"uid":11097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:08:10.000Z","msg":"安你老母<br />\n平你老母<br />\n屌臭你老母"},{"pid":"33433ae5d6f9a1fec9dc88bfb45bf074b06ca8fc","tid":2339292,"uid":145248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"58a1242d9ab680a5dbf043bb34f635ec89b5f08c","tid":2339292,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:09:35.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"c765044de0da373d908ac2dd86f73d747ceb46e9","tid":2339292,"uid":269159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/an7SzEK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fan7SzEK.gif&h=59df642d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af71348a8aeb32500f65efe711aea56f5b4f3925","tid":2339292,"uid":121125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0a05e6d3f935aed33fae83c1b2469e2002c634","tid":2339292,"uid":36152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"簡直係笑話，唔出聲冇人話佢啞"},{"pid":"8185ef5d786a5725709bc3641aafd847d2cd0149","tid":2339292,"uid":311267,"like":1,"disl